{% comment %}
  LP — Garanzie (B2C landing page)

  Code-only LP element. 4 pillar items + 5 guarantee cards.
  Icons are referenced directly from Shopify CDN URLs preserved from Horizon.
  Edit copy / icons by changing the values inline.
{% endcomment %}

{{ 'lp-garanzie.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="lp-gz">

  <div class="lp-gz__top">
    <div class="lp-gz__top-inner">
      <p class="lp-gz__top-headline">PENSATE PER CHI NON SI FERMA MAI.</p>

      <ul class="lp-gz__pillars">

        <li class="lp-gz__pillar">
          <div class="lp-gz__pillar-icon">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/furgoncino.png?v=1777983277" alt="PER I CAMIONISTI" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <p class="lp-gz__pillar-title">PER I CAMIONISTI</p>
          <p class="lp-gz__pillar-text">Progettate per la vita in cabina e per ogni sosta e ripartenza.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="lp-gz__pillar">
          <div class="lp-gz__pillar-icon">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/orologio.png?v=1777983277" alt="PER OGNI GIORNO" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <p class="lp-gz__pillar-title">PER OGNI GIORNO</p>
          <p class="lp-gz__pillar-text">Dal lavoro al tempo libero. Versatili, pratiche e sempre pronte.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="lp-gz__pillar">
          <div class="lp-gz__pillar-icon">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/italia.png?v=1777976336" alt="100% MADE IN ITALY" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <p class="lp-gz__pillar-title">100% MADE IN ITALY</p>
          <p class="lp-gz__pillar-text">Qualità artigianale italiana, materiali selezionati e controllo totale.</p>
        </li>

        <li class="lp-gz__pillar">
          <div class="lp-gz__pillar-icon">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/clienti.png?v=1777983277" alt="APPROVATE DA OLTRE 1200 CAMIONISTI" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <p class="lp-gz__pillar-title">APPROVATE DA OLTRE 1200 CAMIONISTI</p>
          <p class="lp-gz__pillar-text">Migliaia di autisti le hanno già scelte. Scopri perché.</p>
        </li>

      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="lp-gz__bottom">
    <div class="lp-gz__bottom-inner">
      <p class="lp-gz__eyebrow">ACQUISTA SENZA PENSIERI</p>
      <h2 class="lp-gz__h2">LE NOSTRE GARANZIE</h2>

      <ul class="lp-gz__cards">

        <li class="lp-gz__card">
          <div class="lp-gz__card-icon">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/scudo.png?v=1777976336" alt="3 ANNI DI GARANZIA" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="lp-gz__card-body">
            <h3 class="lp-gz__card-title">3 ANNI DI GARANZIA</h3>
            <p class="lp-gz__card-text">Acquistale oggi e indossale per anni. Se c'è un problema, lo risolviamo noi.</p>
            <span class="lp-gz__card-badge">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m8 12 3 3 5-6"/></svg>
              <span class="lp-gz__card-badge-txt">1095 GIORNI<br>COPERTI</span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="lp-gz__card">
          <div class="lp-gz__card-icon">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/reso_gratuito.png?v=1777983277" alt="CAMBIO TAGLIA GRATUITO" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="lp-gz__card-body">
            <h3 class="lp-gz__card-title">CAMBIO TAGLIA GRATUITO</h3>
            <p class="lp-gz__card-text">Se non è la taglia giusta, la cambiamo noi. Gratis.</p>
            <span class="lp-gz__card-badge">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m8 12 3 3 5-6"/></svg>
              <span class="lp-gz__card-badge-txt">SENZA COSTI<br>AGGIUNTIVI</span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="lp-gz__card">
          <div class="lp-gz__card-icon">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/furgoncino.png?v=1777983277" alt="SPEDIZIONE GRATUITA 1-2 GIORNI" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="lp-gz__card-body">
            <h3 class="lp-gz__card-title">SPEDIZIONE GRATUITA 1-2 GIORNI</h3>
            <p class="lp-gz__card-text">Ordina prima delle 19:00, spediamo il giorno stesso. Consegna in 1-2 giorni lavorativi.</p>
            <span class="lp-gz__card-badge">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m8 12 3 3 5-6"/></svg>
              <span class="lp-gz__card-badge-txt">VELOCE E<br>TRACCIATA</span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="lp-gz__card">
          <div class="lp-gz__card-icon">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/carta_di_credito.png?v=1777983277" alt="PAGA IN 3 RATE SENZA INTERESSI" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="lp-gz__card-body">
            <h3 class="lp-gz__card-title">PAGA IN 3 RATE SENZA INTERESSI</h3>
            <p class="lp-gz__card-text">Scegli Klarna o PayPal al checkout e paga in 3 comode rate, senza interessi.</p>
            <span class="lp-gz__card-badge">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m8 12 3 3 5-6"/></svg>
              <span class="lp-gz__card-badge-txt">100% SICURO<br>E GARANTITO</span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="lp-gz__card">
          <div class="lp-gz__card-icon">
            <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0960/9527/3303/files/assistenza_clienti.png?v=1777983277" alt="ASSISTENZA DIRETTA" loading="lazy">
          </div>
          <div class="lp-gz__card-body">
            <h3 class="lp-gz__card-title">ASSISTENZA DIRETTA</h3>
            <p class="lp-gz__card-text">Parli con noi, non con un call center. Siamo camionisti come te, ti capiamo davvero.</p>
            <span class="lp-gz__card-badge">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="m8 12 3 3 5-6"/></svg>
              <span class="lp-gz__card-badge-txt">SEMPRE AL<br>TUO FIANCO</span>
            </span>
          </div>
        </li>

      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>
